data.description: Great close in country cutie! Lakes, rivers, mountain biking, hiking, you name it this location has it! This 3bed/2bath one level home offers a HUGE master suite recently remodeled, open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and a covered front porch to enjoy the mountain views. With low property taxes on .41 acre lot this property has room for RV or boat parking. Don't miss the opportunity to enjoy easy country living!
